outputs.output_descr: A system of high quality vocational training and extension services in agriculture is operational that results in improved productivity, incomes and livelihoods of the rural population.

Quality of vocational education improved, sustainability of the partner Vocational Education and Training (VET) Colleges enhanced and the VET system expanded through linking it with innovative economic development and professional initiatives.

project_descr: Income Generation and Employment through Skills Development
